Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course

Class Course

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course.Activity
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course.Course
  • public class Course
extends Activity
    Course is a holder for course information. It can hold, return, and set the course name, title, section, credit hours, the instructor's unity id, meeting days, and the starting and end time. Includes methods to check if other Course objects are equivalent. Subclass to Activity class.
    Author:
    Raphael Phillips
